   <text>
      <body>
         <div xml:lang="en" type="translation">
            <ab>Apollonides to Zenon, greeting. They have taken away 3 more pigs on the margin of the list supplied by you, so that there are 53. These [three] I have left behind for Dionysios in the village. They are of middle size [half grown?]. And I have supplied an artab of barley until they may reach you.
			Good-bye.		Year 32, Phamenoth 1.
 [Verso:] 				To Zenon.
</ab>
